('services','unisex-salon','Unisex Salon','Full-service unisex salon. Hero must show stylish interiors and a clear Book Appointment CTA. Show service menu by category (hair, skin, nails), stylist team, packages, and walk-in vs appointment options.','espresso brown, blush, gold accent, cream','Stylist, blow-dry, balayage, manicure, pedicure, facial, package, walk-in, family salon','salon-interior, stylist-at-work, after-look-portrait','{announcement_bar,hero,category_grid,image_with_text,testimonials,featured_products,newsletter}','editorial salon photography, mirror reflections, warm tungsten light',210),
('services','hair-stylist','Independent Hair Stylist','Solo hair stylist or freelance creative. Hero must feel personal, portfolio-led, premium. Show signature looks, before/after, home-visit toggle, and direct DM booking.','jet black, hot pink accent, soft cream','Cut, colour, balayage, keratin, bridal hair, home visit, signature look','stylist-portrait, signature-cut, before-after','{announcement_bar,hero,image_with_text,testimonials,featured_products,newsletter,contact_form}','high-fashion portrait photography, dramatic lighting, hero close-ups',211),
