('services','spa-wellness','Spa & Wellness Centre','Luxury day spa or wellness retreat. Hero must feel serene, sensorial, premium. Show signature treatments, couple suites, membership tiers, and gift cards.','warm beige, sage, copper, soft white','Aromatherapy, signature massage, couple suite, hammam, day pass, membership','calm-treatment-room, oil-pouring, serene-portrait','{announcement_bar,hero,image_with_text,featured_products,testimonials,values,newsletter}','soft-focus spa photography, candle glow, sumptuous textures',213),
('services','nail-studio','Nail Studio','Modern nail bar / nail art studio. Hero must feel playful, colourful, Instagrammable. Show nail-art gallery, extensions menu, party packages, and walk-in slots.','soft pink, lilac, neon accent, cream','Gel, extensions, nail art, French, ombre, party, walk-in, instant-book','nail-art-closeup, hands-styled, studio-flatlay','{announcement_bar,hero,featured_products,image_with_text,testimonials,usp_strip,newsletter}','high-saturation product macro, pastel backgrounds, playful props',214),
